SUMMARY:Dot’s Cafe
DESCRIPTION:PDX Silent Book Club\nCome anytime\, bring any book book you're reading :).\nNo pressure to socialize\, you can just dive into your book if you want.\nThe first half hour we'll get comfortable\, get to know each other\, order some food/ drinks.\nThen get down to reading :).\nNo pressure to read\, come and hang out!\nCan't wait to meet you!
